title: Matt McMaster intro
text:
Broadcasting and sports are my passion. I love both and lucky enough have been able to make it my profession. I currently work KLIN Radio as a sports reporter and co host on the Husker Hour radio show that airs every Saturday. I am a
tenacious worker who looks to learn and improve my skills at every
opportunity that I get. I enjoy working with others and not only
achieving individual success but more importantly team success.
